query:
-- Get or create Sacramento County agency
INSERT IGNORE INTO counties (name, state, usesStateProtocols, protocolVersion, createdAt)
VALUES ('Sacramento County EMS Agency', 'California', 0, '2025', NOW());

SET @sac_id = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name LIKE '%Sacramento County%' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1);

-- Insert Sacramento County EMS Adult Treatment Policies (8000 series)
INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, protocolEffectiveDate, protocolYear, createdAt)
VALUES 
(@sac_id, '8001', 'Allergic Reaction / Anaphylaxis', 'Medical', 'Sacramento County EMS Treatment Policy for Allergic Reaction and Anaphylaxis. Epinephrine, diphenhydramine, and supportive care.', 'https://dhs.saccounty.gov/PUB/EMS/Documents/PoliciesProceduresProtocols/8000/PP-8001.pdf', '2025-06-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sac_id, '8002', 'Diabetic Emergencies', 'Medical', 'Sacramento County EMS Treatment Policy for Diabetic Emergencies. Hypoglycemia treatment with dextrose and glucagon.', 'https://dhs.saccounty.gov/PUB/EMS/Documents/PoliciesProceduresProtocols/8000/PP-8002.pdf', '2025-06-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sac_id, '8003', 'Seizures', 'Medical', 'Sacramento County EMS Treatment Policy for Seizures. Benzodiazepine administration and airway protection.', 'https://dhs.saccounty.gov/PUB/EMS/Documents/PoliciesProceduresProtocols/8000/PP-8003.pdf', '2025-06-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sac_id, '8004', 'Suspected Narcotic Overdose', 'Medical', 'Sacramento County EMS Treatment Policy for Suspected Narcotic Overdose. Naloxone administration.', 'https://dhs.saccounty.gov/PUB/EMS/Documents/PoliciesProceduresProtocols/8000/PP-8004.pdf', '2025-06-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sac_id, '8007', 'Abdominal Pain', 'Medical', 'Sacramento County EMS Treatment Policy for Abdominal Pain. Assessment and pain management.', 'https://dhs.saccounty.gov/PUB/EMS/Documents/PoliciesProceduresProtocols/8000/PP-8007.pdf', '2025-06-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sac_id, '8015', 'Trauma', 'Trauma', 'Sacramento County EMS Treatment Policy for Trauma. Primary survey, hemorrhage control, and transport criteria.', 'https://dhs.saccounty.gov/PUB/EMS/Documents/PoliciesProceduresProtocols/8000/PP-8015.pdf', '2025-06-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sac_id, '8017', 'Dystonic Reaction', 'Medical', 'Sacramento County EMS Treatment Policy for Dystonic Reaction. Diphenhydramine administration.', 'https://dhs.saccounty.gov/PUB/EMS/Documents/PoliciesProceduresProtocols/8000/PP-8017.pdf', '2025-06-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sac_id, '8018', 'Overdose and/or Poison Ingestion', 'Medical', 'Sacramento County EMS Treatment Policy for Overdose and Poison Ingestion. Supportive care and specific antidotes.', 'https://dhs.saccounty.gov/PUB/EMS/Documents/PoliciesProceduresProtocols/8000/PP-8018.pdf', '2025-06-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sac_id, '8020', 'Respiratory Distress: Airway Management', 'Respiratory', 'Sacramento County EMS Treatment Policy for Airway Management. BLS and ALS airway techniques.', 'https://dhs.saccounty.gov/PUB/EMS/Documents/PoliciesProceduresProtocols/8000/PP-8020.pdf', '2025-06-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sac_id, '8024', 'Cardiac Dysrhythmias', 'Cardiac', 'Sacramento County EMS Treatment Policy for Cardiac Dysrhythmias. Bradycardia, tachycardia, and cardiac arrest algorithms.', 'https://dhs.saccounty.gov/PUB/EMS/Documents/PoliciesProceduresProtocols/8000/PP-8024.pdf', '2025-06-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sac_id, '8025', 'Burns', 'Trauma', 'Sacramento County EMS Treatment Policy for Burns. Burn assessment, cooling, and fluid resuscitation.', 'https://dhs.saccounty.gov/PUB/EMS/Documents/PoliciesProceduresProtocols/8000/PP-8025.pdf', '2025-06-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sac_id, '8026', 'Respiratory Distress', 'Respiratory', 'Sacramento County EMS Treatment Policy for Respiratory Distress. Assessment-based treatment and bronchodilators.', 'https://dhs.saccounty.gov/PUB/EMS/Documents/PoliciesProceduresProtocols/8000/PP-8026.pdf', '2025-06-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sac_id, '8027', 'Symptomatic Nerve Agent Exposure', 'Environmental', 'Sacramento County EMS Treatment Policy for Nerve Agent Exposure. Atropine and pralidoxime.', 'https://dhs.saccounty.gov/PUB/EMS/Documents/PoliciesProceduresProtocols/8000/PP-8027.pdf', '2025-06-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sac_id, '8028', 'Environmental Emergencies', 'Environmental', 'Sacramento County EMS Treatment Policy for Environmental Emergencies. Hyperthermia, hypothermia, and frostbite.', 'https://dhs.saccounty.gov/PUB/EMS/Documents/PoliciesProceduresProtocols/8000/PP-8028.pdf', '2025-06-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sac_id, '8029', 'Hazardous Materials', 'Environmental', 'Sacramento County EMS Treatment Policy for Hazardous Materials. Decontamination and supportive care.', 'https://dhs.saccounty.gov/PUB/EMS/Documents/PoliciesProceduresProtocols/8000/PP-8029.pdf', '2025-06-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sac_id, '8030', 'Discomfort-Pain of Suspected Cardiac Origin', 'Cardiac', 'Sacramento County EMS Treatment Policy for Chest Pain/ACS. 12-lead ECG, aspirin, nitroglycerin, and STEMI activation.', 'https://dhs.saccounty.gov/PUB/EMS/Documents/PoliciesProceduresProtocols/8000/PP-8030.pdf', '2025-06-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sac_id, '8031', 'Non-Traumatic Cardiac Arrest', 'Cardiac', 'Sacramento County EMS Treatment Policy for Non-Traumatic Cardiac Arrest. CPR, defibrillation, and ACLS medications.', 'https://dhs.saccounty.gov/PUB/EMS/Documents/PoliciesProceduresProtocols/8000/PP-8031.pdf', '2025-06-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sac_id, '8032', 'Traumatic Cardiac Arrest', 'Trauma', 'Sacramento County EMS Treatment Policy for Traumatic Cardiac Arrest. Hemorrhage control and rapid transport.', 'https://dhs.saccounty.gov/PUB/EMS/Documents/PoliciesProceduresProtocols/8000/PP-8032.pdf', '2025-06-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sac_id, '8038', 'Shock', 'Medical', 'Sacramento County EMS Treatment Policy for Shock. Fluid resuscitation and vasopressor support.', 'https://dhs.saccounty.gov/PUB/EMS/Documents/PoliciesProceduresProtocols/8000/PP-8038.pdf', '2025-06-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sac_id, '8042', 'Childbirth', 'Obstetrical', 'Sacramento County EMS Treatment Policy for Childbirth. Normal delivery and complications.', 'https://dhs.saccounty.gov/PUB/EMS/Documents/PoliciesProceduresProtocols/8000/PP-8042.pdf', '2025-06-01', 2025, NOW());
